			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load up CTY_Main_A\r\nopen the debug book and set the prisoners to saved\r\nOpen ReCon and use \"oe low_foundry_fundangofollower\"\r\nalso set up \"Roll horrible\"\r\nteleport to -1982; -1; 420 and pick a fight with nearby enemies. Start killing them until a killswitch drops.\r\nAttempt to disarm one - because of roll horrilbe it will fail\r\nobserve the consequences\r\nFinish the fight\r\nthe dialog should auto-start"
				},
